    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Dominus vir
                        gloriosissimus <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/373"
                            >Grimoald</persName> Dei previdentia Langobardorum gentis <rs
                            key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, motus Dei omnipotentis misericordia et
                        pro redemptione animae nostrae, per <rs key="#Intercessory"
                            >postulatione</rs>
                        <persName key="#Marepahis #Intercessory" ref="#people/1997">Laupi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marepahis">mari pahis</rs> nostri, concedimus in <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries #Slave_labour #Freeborn"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/84">Beati Benedicti</orgName> quod situm est in
                            <rs key="#Castle">castro</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Castle #Monasteries" ref="#places/109">Casino</placeName>,
                        ubi vir reverentissimus <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/375">
                            Gisolfus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> preesse videtur, omne <rs
                            key="#Slave #Slave_labour">servos</rs> qui fuerunt ipsius monasterii
                        cum <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Work_and_workers #Slave_labour #Freeborn"
                            >oxoribus suis quae fuerunt libere</rs> cum filiis, filiabus suis, tam
                        qui tempore domni <persName key="#Marquis/duke" ref="#people/158"
                            >Gisulfi</persName> quam et domni <persName key="#Marquis/duke"
                            ref="#people/374">Liutprandi</persName> vel domni sanctae ac dulcis
                        memoriae <persName key="#Marquis/duke #Princeps" ref="#people/303">genitoris
                            nostri</persName> et nostro felicissimo tempore sunt aut fuerint
                        compulti et legibus nostrae potestati tenuerunt aut tenuerint, in eam
                        videlicet rationem ut amodo et deinceps per hoc nostrum roboretur preceptum
                        tam vos, reverentissime Gisolfe abba, quam et posteres vestri qui in eundem
                        sacrum prefuerint cenobium, omnes illos servos cum psis uxoribus et cum
                        filiis, filiabus suis, qualiter superius legitur, habere et possidere
                        valeatis, et a nullo ex nostris iudicibus, is est comitibus, gastaldis vel a
                        quibuscumque gentibus habeatis aliquam requisitionem, sed perpetuis
                        temporibus habere et possidere valeatis. Quod vero preceptum concessimus ex
                        iussione nostrae potestatis scripsi ego <persName key="#Notary"><name
                                ref="Benedictus">Benedictus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actum <placeName key="#Cities #Palatium"
                            ref="#places/110">Beneventi</placeName> in sacratissimo <rs
                            key="#Palatium">Palatio</rs> nono anno, mense IIo, quinta
                        indictione feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
